  <brief_title>A Study to Determine the Location of the Blind Spot and the Macula-disc Centre Distance on a Fundus Photograph</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study to Develop Both a Novel Method for Evaluating the True Size of a Retinal Object on Fundus Photographs and a New Reaction-time Based Method for Studying the Visual Field on Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
