  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study is aimed to develop a new reaction-time based method for examining the visual field
      and to study the effect of refractive error on the magnification of a fundus photograph in
      order to evaluate the true size of a retinal feature.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
